objects.name: story
objects.string:
Einst wurden vier Elemente erschaffen, mit dem Ziel die Welt zu bereichern. 

Die Erde verbreitete sich als fruchtbaren Lebensraum, 
die Luft gab sich als Quelle des Überlebens und das Wasser umfasst diese Gaben. 

Das Feuer, nun ja ... es durchkreuzt seither die Welt auf der Suche nach der Bestimmung.

Kannst du sie finden?
Doch respektiere unterwegs die anderen Elemente.

eventsFunctionsExtensions.author: westboy, daliyoucefmedakram@gmail.com
eventsFunctionsExtensions.description:
Animate the text to simulate it being written character by character (also called "typewriter" effect), with a customizable time between each character. Useful for dialogue scenes or visual novels.

Add the behavior to a Text object (or BBText object) and choose the interval between characters.

* When the text changes, the automatic typing starts again from the beginning with the new text.
* You can change the speed of the text typing by changing the interval with events.
* Use a condition to check if the typing finished.
* You can also pause the typing and resume it after.
eventsFunctionsExtensions.fullName: Auto typing animation for texts ("typewriter" effect)

eventsFunctionsExtensions.author: Gustavo Marciano
eventsFunctionsExtensions.description:
Set the depth (Z-order) of the instance to the value of its Y position in the scene, creating an illusion of depth. The origin point of the object is used to determine the Z-order.

Useful for isometric games, 2D games with a "Top-Down" view, RPG...
eventsFunctionsExtensions.name: YSort
eventsFunctionsExtensions.shortDescription: Create an illusion of depth by setting the Z-order based on the Y position of the object. Useful for isometric games, 2D games with a "Top-Down" view, RPG...
